<h1>Introduction</h1>

<p>The Bladesin is a quirky build of the Assassin that uses her rarely-used Blade Trap skills. These Traps are based on her physical Damage so having a solid weapon is highly recommended. Overall this character struggles through the game but with high end gear can be playable.</p>

<h1>Quick Reference</h1>

<h2>Skill Build</h2>

<p>The following section shows the core skills for the Bladesin. For a detailed breakdown of all core and optional skills as well as the recommended order for allocating skill points, refer to the Skills section of this guide.</p>

<ol>
<li>1 point to all prerequisites</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2BladeFury@@@ - Main Damage Skill, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2Venom@@@ - Increases overall Damage, required</li>
<li>1 points to @@@D2MindBlast@@@ - @@@D2Conversion@@@ and Crowd Control, required</li>
<li>1 points to @@@D2CloakOfShadows@@@ - Crowd Control, required</li>
<li>1+ points to @@@D2Fade@@@ - Increased Resistances and Physical Damage Reduction, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2DeathSentry@@@ - Useful for blowing up dead corpses and AOE, required</li>
</ol>

